[{"Code":"en","Title":"Transaction and settlement statuses","Slug":"transaction-status","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4a-pgsm5q-020\">Use this reference to read the pair of fields <code>transaction_status</code> and <code>settlement_status</code> you see in the Dashboard, API responses, and reports.</p><div class=\"image-view-figure\"><figure data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-wtbbqj-021\" class=\"figure\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\"><img data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-6tzl1x-022\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/status_transitions.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Flowchart showing possible transitions between transaction statuses and settlement statuses.\" width=\"1000\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:1000px;height:auto;\"><figcaption data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-id47z4-103\" style=\"width:1000px;\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-1otz7q-104\">     </p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5ha-j4fajp-153\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zz8o-zbwbfg-176\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zzjb-iou0cu-178\"></p><p><figcaption data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-ne6ycv-023\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-ygxz0o-105\">High-level flow of status transitions</p></figcaption></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zzjb-ua9520-179\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zz8o-x71po6-177\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5ha-4vyff6-154\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-s81d7k-106\"></p></figcaption></figure></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-a2tjwq-024\">Money-in (Payments)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-62o4le-025\">The table below maps each payment phase to its <code>transaction_status</code> and <code>settlement_status</code>.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"985\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:985px;width:985px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:170px;\"><col style=\"width:205px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-ba5wsc-107\">Phase</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-7v3lya-108\">Transaction Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-d25jom-109\">Settlement Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-1286rg-110\">Meaning</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-abxyal-111\">Payment success</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-pb6wb8-112\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-qle73t-113\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-ozpivo-114\">Funds captured; will be settled automatically on <code>settlement_date</code>.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciw915n-qrjj5j-033\">Settlement complete — normal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-rl4xuq-115\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-maog2y-116\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-d1heg6-117\">Funds posted on the scheduled settlement date.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-ht6hki-118\">Settlement complete — early</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-41yhll-119\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-499i4l-120\"><strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-u93ucf-121\">Funds posted <em>before</em> the scheduled settlement date.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-nb8ktn-122\">Cancelled before settlement</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-i54tht-123\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-srvqk4-124\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-fxx5d3-125\">Payment voided before any ledger posting.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwa8e0-g1ao3k-035\">Reversal after settlement</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-1p5oj9-126\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-nja127-127\"><strong>SETTLED</strong> / <strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-tyl1wa-128\">Transaction reversed manually after settlement.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mciw7e4d-4qi2or-026\">Money-out (Payouts &amp; Refunds)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4d-l8ijmx-027\">The same two fields apply to outgoing funds. Interpret them using the table below.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"995\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:995px;width:995px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:171px;\"><col style=\"width:214px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-g4bk2l-129\">Phase</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-v6dgwg-130\">Transaction Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-e9jzu4-131\">Settlement Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-ebiu4l-132\">Meaning</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-hkiwvl-133\">Payout created</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-mihfga-134\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-d2qfdv-135\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-qzt9z9-136\">Transaction created; processing with partner.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-oohysy-137\">Failed payout</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-efzlrx-138\"><strong>FAILED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-9e3xj7-139\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-hmotm2-140\">Partner rejected the payout.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-siu7ju-141\">Payout success</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-yd5b85-142\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-1yjeck-143\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-infn5h-144\">Funds debited and ledger movement completed.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-22e41p-145\">Cancelled before settlement</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-a4lkp3-146\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-qplu04-147\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-gcaitp-148\">Transaction cancelled before settlement.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-8wwnve-149\">Reversal after settlement</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-4xtnet-150\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5by-kpudbz-151\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5by-4ftgqy-152\">Payout manually reversed during reconciliation.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mciw88ns-leek3e-031\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Transaction and settlement statuses","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Status transaksi & settlement","Slug":"transaction-status","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs409qi-q3yjfl-322\">Gunakan referensi ini untuk membaca sepasang bidang <code>transaction_status</code> dan <code>settlement_status</code> Anda lihat di Dasbor, respons API, dan laporan.</p><div class=\"image-view-figure\"><figure data-block-id=\"mcs409qk-1689r7-323\" class=\"figure\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\"><img data-block-id=\"mcs409qk-ju2rmt-324\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/status_transitions.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Flowchart showing possible transitions between transaction statuses and settlement statuses.\" width=\"1000\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:1000px;height:auto;\"><figcaption data-block-id=\"mcs409ql-r86s0t-325\" style=\"width:1000px;\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ql-43cnuo-326\">     </p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ql-985pnc-327\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qm-9dk9uk-328\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qm-3u616k-329\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qm-8svcnr-330\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs40jqq-zfpa67-391\"></p><p><figcaption data-block-id=\"mcs409qm-fn83xv-331\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qm-u3gp1a-332\">Alur transisi status tingkat tinggi</p></figcaption></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs40jqr-ot6w0o-392\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qm-s6iqn3-333\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qn-ce24o7-334\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qp-nrx0rh-335\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qp-n6gy1b-336\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qp-shxr74-337\"></p></figcaption></figure></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs409qp-58q1py-338\">Money-in (Pembayaran)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qq-keq12b-339\">Tabel di bawah ini memetakan setiap fase pembayaran ke <code>transaction_status</code> dan <code>settlement_status</code>.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"985\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:985px;width:985px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:170px;\"><col style=\"width:205px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qs-5c2whe-340\">Fase</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qw-vmw3td-341\">Status Transaksi</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qx-lo1tan-342\">Status Penyelesaian</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qy-andk70-343\">Arti</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409qz-myxfqk-344\">Keberhasilan pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r0-nmozqg-345\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r2-fs7xoh-346\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r5-8cyx43-347\">Dana ditangkap; akan diselesaikan secara otomatis pada <code>settlement_date</code>.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r5-bmo3ln-348\">Penyelesaian selesai — normal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r6-lmj9le-349\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r7-zg324s-350\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r7-2tfi5i-351\">Dana yang diposting pada tanggal penyelesaian yang dijadwalkan.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r8-v1aq86-352\">Penyelesaian selesai — lebih awal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r8-ohtn9l-353\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409r9-nyuxu2-354\"><strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ra-fr7v0d-355\">Dana yang diposting <em>sebelum</em> tanggal penyelesaian yang dijadwalkan.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ra-oq8rl3-356\">Dibatalkan sebelum penyelesaian</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rb-hs9t13-357\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rb-4rpm6l-358\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rc-rphedc-359\">Pembayaran dibatalkan sebelum posting buku besar.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rd-bzh78q-360\">Pembalikan setelah penyelesaian</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rd-vvcx0l-361\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rf-294fb6-362\"><strong>SETTLED</strong> / <strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rh-nco5hy-363\">Transaksi dibalik secara manual setelah penyelesaian.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs409rh-h35qcv-364\">Money-out (Pembayaran &amp; Pengembalian Dana)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rh-18rwm8-365\">Dua bidang yang sama berlaku untuk dana keluar. Tafsirkan menggunakan tabel di bawah ini.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"995\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:995px;width:995px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:171px;\"><col style=\"width:214px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ri-1esyyi-366\">Fase</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rj-mwmwpw-367\">Status Transaksi</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rk-v41lhq-368\">Status Penyelesaian</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rl-w294xd-369\">Arti</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rl-y051pt-370\">Pembayaran dibuat</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rm-dm832e-371\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rm-l9km9i-372\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rn-x5pnaz-373\">Transaksi dibuat; pemrosesan dengan mitra.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ro-9804qw-374\">Pembayaran gagal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ro-llthsu-375\"><strong>FAILED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rp-5naicf-376\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rr-ox2eo2-377\">Mitra menolak pembayaran.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rs-tzdim2-378\">Keberhasilan pembayaran</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rt-jvx429-379\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rv-limmui-380\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rv-5oiqee-381\">Dana didebet dan pergerakan buku besar selesai.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rw-jwg2p4-382\">Dibatalkan sebelum penyelesaian</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs41xol-p54yr3-397\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rx-41v2qc-384\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ry-fofly0-385\">Transaksi dibatalkan sebelum penyelesaian.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409ry-71jyvn-386\">Pembalikan setelah penyelesaian</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rz-06prad-387\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409rz-vujsph-388\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs409s0-mmsiuw-389\">Pembayaran dibalik secara manual selama rekonsiliasi.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mcs409s0-8az1ig-390\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Status transaksi & settlement","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"สถานะธุรกรรมและการชำระบัญชี","Slug":"transaction-status","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4a-pgsm5q-020\">ใช้ข้อมูลอ้างอิงนี้เพื่ออ่านคู่ฟิลด์ <code>transaction_status</code> และ <code>settlement_status</code> ที่คุณเห็นใน Dashboard, การตอบกลับของ API, และรายงานต่างๆ</p><div class=\"image-view-figure\"><figure data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-wtbbqj-021\" class=\"figure\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\"><img data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-6tzl1x-022\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/status_transitions.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Flowchart showing possible transitions between transaction statuses and settlement statuses.\" width=\"1000\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:1000px;height:auto;\"><figcaption data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-id47z4-103\" style=\"width:1000px;\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-1otz7q-104\">     </p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5ha-j4fajp-153\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zz8o-zbwbfg-176\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zzjb-iou0cu-178\"></p><p></p><figcaption data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-ne6ycv-023\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-ygxz0o-105\">โฟลว์ระดับสูงของการเปลี่ยนสถานะ</p></figcaption><p></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zzjb-ua9520-179\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zz8o-x71po6-177\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5ha-4vyff6-154\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-s81d7k-106\"></p></figcaption></figure></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-a2tjwq-024\">เงินเข้า (Payments)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-62o4le-025\">ตารางด้านล่างแสดงการจับคู่แต่ละขั้นตอนการชำระเงินกับ <code>transaction_status</code> และ <code>settlement_status</code></p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"985\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:985px;width:985px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:170px;\"><col style=\"width:205px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-ba5wsc-107\">ขั้นตอน</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-7v3lya-108\">Transaction Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-d25jom-109\">Settlement Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-1286rg-110\">ความหมาย</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-abxyal-111\">การชำระเงินสำเร็จ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-pb6wb8-112\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-qle73t-113\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-ozpivo-114\">ได้รับเงินแล้ว; จะถูกชำระเงินโดยอัตโนมัติใน <code>settlement_date</code>.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciw915n-qrjj5j-033\">การชำระเงินเสร็จสมบูรณ์ — ปกติ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-rl4xuq-115\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-maog2y-116\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-d1heg6-117\">เงินถูกบันทึกในบัญชีตามวันที่กำหนดสำหรับการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-ht6hki-118\">การชำระเงินเสร็จสมบูรณ์ — เร็ว</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-41yhll-119\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-499i4l-120\"><strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-u93ucf-121\">เงินถูกบันทึกในบัญชี <em>ก่อน</em> วันที่กำหนดสำหรับการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-nb8ktn-122\">ถูกยกเลิกก่อนการชำระเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-i54tht-123\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-srvqk4-124\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-fxx5d3-125\">การชำระเงินถูกยกเลิกก่อนการบันทึกบัญชีใดๆ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwa8e0-g1ao3k-035\">การยกเลิกหลังจากชำระเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-1p5oj9-126\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-nja127-127\"><strong>SETTLED</strong> / <strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-tyl1wa-128\">ธุรกรรมถูกยกเลิกด้วยตนเองหลังจากการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mciw7e4d-4qi2or-026\">เงินออก (Payouts &amp; Refunds)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4d-l8ijmx-027\">สองฟิลด์เดียวกันนี้ใช้กับเงินที่ส่งออกไป โปรดตีความโดยใช้ตารางด้านล่าง</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"995\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:995px;width:995px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:171px;\"><col style=\"width:214px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-g4bk2l-129\">ขั้นตอน</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-v6dgwg-130\">Transaction Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-e9jzu4-131\">Settlement Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-ebiu4l-132\">ความหมาย</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-hkiwvl-133\">สร้าง Payout</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-mihfga-134\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-d2qfdv-135\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-qzt9z9-136\">สร้างธุรกรรมแล้ว; กำลังดำเนินการกับพันธมิตร</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-oohysy-137\">Payout ล้มเหลว</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-efzlrx-138\"><strong>FAILED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-9e3xj7-139\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-hmotm2-140\">พันธมิตรปฏิเสธ Payout</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-siu7ju-141\">Payout สำเร็จ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-yd5b85-142\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-1yjeck-143\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-infn5h-144\">หักเงินแล้วและการเคลื่อนไหวของบัญชีเสร็จสมบูรณ์</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-22e41p-145\">ถูกยกเลิกก่อนการชำระเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-a4lkp3-146\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-qplu04-147\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-gcaitp-148\">ธุรกรรมถูกยกเลิกก่อนการชำระเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-8wwnve-149\">การยกเลิกหลังจากชำระเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-4xtnet-150\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5by-kpudbz-151\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5by-4ftgqy-152\">Payout ถูกยกเลิกด้วยตนเองระหว่างการกระทบยอด</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mciw88ns-leek3e-031\"></p>","SeoTitle":"สถานะธุรกรรมและการชำระบัญชี","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Estados de Transacción y Liquidación","Slug":"transaction-status","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4a-pgsm5q-020\">Utilice esta referencia para leer el par de campos <code>transaction_status</code> y <code>settlement_status</code> que ve en el Dashboard, las responses de la API y los reportes.</p><div class=\"image-view-figure\"><figure data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-wtbbqj-021\" class=\"figure\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\"><img data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-6tzl1x-022\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/status_transitions.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"Flowchart showing possible transitions between transaction statuses and settlement statuses.\" width=\"1000\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:1000px;height:auto;\"><figcaption data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-id47z4-103\" style=\"width:1000px;\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-1otz7q-104\">     </p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5ha-j4fajp-153\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zz8o-zbwbfg-176\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zzjb-iou0cu-178\"></p><p></p><figcaption data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-ne6ycv-023\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-ygxz0o-105\">Flujo de alto nivel de las transiciones de estado</p></figcaption><p></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zzjb-ua9520-179\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs3zz8o-x71po6-177\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5ha-4vyff6-154\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5be-s81d7k-106\"></p></figcaption></figure></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-a2tjwq-024\">Ingreso de fondos (Pagos)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4b-62o4le-025\">La siguiente tabla mapea cada fase de Pago con su <code>transaction_status</code> y <code>settlement_status</code>.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"985\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:985px;width:985px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:170px;\"><col style=\"width:205px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-ba5wsc-107\">Fase</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-7v3lya-108\">Transaction Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-d25jom-109\">Settlement Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-1286rg-110\">Significado</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-abxyal-111\">Éxito del Pago</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-pb6wb8-112\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bu-qle73t-113\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-ozpivo-114\">Fondos capturados; se liquidarán automáticamente en la <code>settlement_date</code>.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciw915n-qrjj5j-033\">Liquidación completada &#x2014; normal</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-rl4xuq-115\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-maog2y-116\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-d1heg6-117\">Fondos registrados en la fecha de liquidación programada.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-ht6hki-118\">Liquidación completada &#x2014; anticipada</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-41yhll-119\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-499i4l-120\"><strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-u93ucf-121\">Fondos registrados <em>antes</em> de la fecha de liquidación programada.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-nb8ktn-122\">Cancelado antes de la liquidación</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-i54tht-123\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-srvqk4-124\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bv-fxx5d3-125\">Pago anulado antes de cualquier registro contable.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwa8e0-g1ao3k-035\">Reversión después de la liquidación</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"170\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-1p5oj9-126\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"205\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-nja127-127\"><strong>SETTLED</strong> / <strong>EARLY_SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-tyl1wa-128\">Transacción revertida manualmente después de la liquidación.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mciw7e4d-4qi2or-026\">Egreso de fondos (Payouts &amp; Reembolsos)</h2><p data-block-id=\"mciw7e4d-l8ijmx-027\">Los mismos dos campos aplican a los fondos salientes. Interprételos utilizando la siguiente tabla.</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"995\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:995px;width:995px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:246px;\"><col style=\"width:171px;\"><col style=\"width:214px;\"><col style=\"width:364px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-g4bk2l-129\">Fase</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-v6dgwg-130\">Transaction Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-e9jzu4-131\">Settlement Status</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-ebiu4l-132\">Significado</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-hkiwvl-133\">Payout creado</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-mihfga-134\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bw-d2qfdv-135\"><strong>PENDING</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-qzt9z9-136\">Transacción creada; procesando con el socio.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-oohysy-137\">Payout fallido</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-efzlrx-138\"><strong>FAILED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-9e3xj7-139\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-hmotm2-140\">El socio rechazó el Payout.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-siu7ju-141\">Payout exitoso</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-yd5b85-142\"><strong>SUCCESS</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-1yjeck-143\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-infn5h-144\">Fondos debitados y movimiento contable completado.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-22e41p-145\">Cancelado antes de la liquidación</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-a4lkp3-146\"><strong>VOIDED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-qplu04-147\"><strong>null</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-gcaitp-148\">Transacción cancelada antes de la liquidación.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"246\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-8wwnve-149\">Reversión después de la liquidación</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"171\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5bx-4xtnet-150\"><strong>REVERSED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"214\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5by-kpudbz-151\"><strong>SETTLED</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"364\"><p data-block-id=\"mciwi5by-4ftgqy-152\">Payout revertido manualmente durante la conciliación.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mciw88ns-leek3e-031\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Estados de Transacción y Liquidación","Description":null}]